  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 2nd level, you can add half your proficiency bonus, rounded down, to any ability check you make with a tool that does not already include your proficiency bonus.</p><p>You also learn how to produce exactly the tool you need: with thieves' tools or artisan's tools, you can magically create one set of artisan's tools in an unoccupied space within 5 feet of you. This creation requires 1 hour of uninterrupted work, which can coincide with a short or long rest. Though the product of magic, the tools are nonmagical, and they vanish when you use this feature again.</p>",
